SimpleCaptcha - A Java library for creating CAPTCHAs based on simplecaptcha available at SourceForge: 

http://simplecaptcha.sourceforge.net

https://sourceforge.net/projects/simplecaptcha/

by James Childers. 

In this fork the following modifications are made:
* project was mavenized
* code was rewritten to use newer jhlabs filters library, which is available on maven central
* JEE/servlets integration was dropped
